---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Επικοινωνία - Updated Typography">

<!-- Top Navigation Bar -->
<nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-md">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center px-8 h-20 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-emerald-900 font-headline">Organic Nutrition</div>
<div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 items-center">
<a class="text-slate-600 hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors font-medium" href="#">Αρχική</a>
<a class="text-slate-600 hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors font-medium" href="#">Υπηρεσίες</a>
<a class="text-slate-600 hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors font-medium" href="#">Κλείσε Ραντεβού</a>
<a class="text-slate-600 hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors font-medium" href="#">Άρθρα</a>
<a class="text-emerald-700 border-b-2 border-emerald-700 pb-1 font-medium" href="#">Επικοινωνία</a>
</div>
<button class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:opacity-90 active:scale-95 transition-all shadow-sm">
            Κλείσε Ραντεβού
        </button>
</div>
</nav>
<main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<header class="mb-20">
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6 tracking-tight">Επικοινωνία</h1>
<p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
            Είμαστε εδώ για να απαντήσουμε σε κάθε σας απορία και να ξεκινήσουμε μαζί το ταξίδι προς μια πιο υγιή και ισορροπημένη ζωή.
        </p>
</header>
<!-- Bento Grid Layout -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
<!-- Contact Info Column -->
<div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-8">
<!-- Info Card 1: Direct Contact -->
<div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-8 text-primary">Στοιχεία Επικοινωνίας</h3>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-secondary-container group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="call">call</span>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-xs font-bold text-outline uppercase tracking-wider font-label">Τηλέφωνο</p>
<p class="text-lg font-medium text-on-surface">+30 210 1234567</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-primary-container group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="mail">mail</span>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-xs font-bold text-outline uppercase tracking-wider font-label">Email</p>
<p class="text-lg font-medium text-on-surface">hello@organicnutrition.gr</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-tertiary-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-tertiary-container group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="location_on">location_on</span>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-xs font-bold text-outline uppercase tracking-wider font-label">Διεύθυνση</p>
<p class="text-lg font-medium text-on-surface">Λεωφόρος Κηφισίας 124, Αθήνα</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Hours Card -->
<div class="bg-primary text-on-primary p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="relative z-10">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6">Ωράριο Λειτουργίας</h3>
<ul class="space-y-3 opacity-90">
<li class="flex justify-between border-b border-on-primary/10 pb-2">
<span>Δευτέρα - Παρασκευή</span>
<span class="font-bold">09:00 - 20:00</span>
</li>
<li class="flex justify-between border-b border-on-primary/10 pb-2">
<span>Σάββατο</span>
<span class="font-bold">10:00 - 15:00</span>
</li>
<li class="flex justify-between">
<span>Κυριακή</span>
<span class="font-bold">Κλειστά</span>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="absolute -right-12 -bottom-12 w-48 h-48 bg-white/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
</div>
<!-- Small Map Placeholder -->
<div class="h-48 w-full rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-high relative">
<img alt="Χάρτης τοποθεσίας" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-50 contrast-125" data-alt="Modern clean map interface showing a minimalist city grid with a soft green pin marker in a high-end district" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDvq8iloyYtD_Qlt4W5_kGFO2cn11iSQDYFIJyImxK6EYSU18GFiCjcSSgeUBNmaAYxtkzOhzdK5qr5eB78FhIW80IHr-VUYMrQ61A62YndqSFpeGZqOmvBfFkJaZSepKIKl8ZCKjGporHgjyWMHJkXiFq-HTP1tHwbsF7VanNd_sYxXKZPIs0Ht_LhFNDIvJ7XJSw0doSOGrg2zGlzMCnHxpJahrFdHpWHTFDzfpKcZn1lMV-CBjMP8xyVHnpDX49H10O7ouOBvJY"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
<div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-4 py-2 rounded-full flex items-center gap-2 shadow-sm cursor-pointer">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="map" data-weight="fill" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">map</span>
<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary font-label">Άνοιγμα στους Χάρτες</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Contact Form Column -->
<div class="lg:col-span-7">
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 md:p-12 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/20">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-8">Στείλτε μας ένα μήνυμα</h2>
<form class="space-y-8">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant px-1 font-label">Ονοματεπώνυμο</label>
<input class="w-full bg-surface-container-high border-none rounded-xl px-4 py-4 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:bg-surface-container-highest transition-all outline-none text-on-surface placeholder:text-outline/60" placeholder="Πώς σας λένε;" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant px-1 font-label">Email</label>
<input class="w-full bg-surface-container-high border-none rounded-xl px-4 py-4 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:bg-surface-container-highest transition-all outline-none text-on-surface placeholder:text-outline/60" placeholder="email@example.com" type="email"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant px-1 font-label">Θέμα</label>
<select class="w-full bg-surface-container-high border-none rounded-xl px-4 py-4 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:bg-surface-container-highest transition-all outline-none text-on-surface">
<option>Γενική Ερώτηση</option>
<option>Κλείσιμο Ραντεβού</option>
<option>Διατροφικό Πρόγραμμα</option>
<option>Συνεργασία</option>
</select>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant px-1 font-label">Μήνυμα</label>
<textarea class="w-full bg-surface-container-high border-none rounded-xl px-4 py-4 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:bg-surface-container-highest transition-all outline-none text-on-surface placeholder:text-outline/60" placeholder="Περιγράψτε τι σας απασχολεί..." rows="5"></textarea>
</div>
<div class="pt-4">
<button class="w-full md:w-auto bg-primary text-on-primary px-12 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-3 hover:shadow-lg active:scale-95 transition-all group" type="submit">
<span>Αποστολή</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" data-icon="send">send</span>
</button>
</div>
</form>
</div>
<div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-secondary-container/30 rounded-xl flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0 bg-primary">
<img alt="Διαιτολόγος" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Close-up portrait of a professional female nutritionist in a bright white clinic smiling warmly with soft natural lighting" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAZ2U8EU-dUYksh1qong_MuBmlRXMlrbyfiZ9oSbRrq08H4KFXEPkA2cNfGHIlGPY-FO4ZsIN-N9y9CI6IfqQh97lxtzhUMc4_-ePsD-EiaouEYKLyiYyjYwiAdgbUxwYnxEdwXvfJrwFUFTldxj4LEq2xrhF02KyEWXRzkAP4KyL5FriMQd-QGkwoKCaFPEC0o5GKMqn7QY6iYLwD1MLvg-svbQVee5rzidvH9m9I4HUM_yrECxHkZfaP1XK8hcmLyhgY8G3Gn25k"/>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-on-secondary-container font-medium leading-relaxed italic">
                        "Η διατροφή δεν είναι στέρηση, είναι αυτοφροντίδα. Θα χαρώ να σας βοηθήσω να βρείτε την ισορροπία που σας ταιριάζει."
                    </p>
<p class="text-primary font-bold mt-2">— Δρ. Ελένη Παπαδοπούλου, Κλινική Διαιτολόγος</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</main>
<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="bg-emerald-900 dark:bg-black w-full pt-16 pb-8">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 px-8 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-50 mb-6">Organic Atelier</h3>
<p class="text-emerald-100/70 leading-relaxed">
                Εξατομικευμένες λύσεις διατροφής βασισμένες σε επιστημονικά δεδομένα και ολιστική προσέγγιση.
            </p>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-emerald-50 font-semibold mb-6">Γρήγοροι Σύνδεσμοι</h4>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li><a class="text-emerald-100/70 hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#">Υπηρεσίες</a></li>
<li><a class="text-emerald-100/70 hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#">Άρθρα Υγείας</a></li>
<li><a class="text-emerald-100/70 hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#">Συνταγές</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-emerald-50 font-semibold mb-6">Νομικά</h4>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li><a class="text-emerald-100/70 hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#">Πολιτική Απορρήτου</a></li>
<li><a class="text-emerald-100/70 hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#">Όροι Χρήσης</a></li>
<li><a class="text-emerald-100/70 hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#">Συχνές Ερωτήσεις</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-emerald-800 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
<p class="text-emerald-100/50 text-sm">© 2024 The Organic Atelier. Με επιφύλαξη παντός δικαιώματος.</p>
<div class="flex gap-6">
<a class="text-emerald-100/50 hover:text-white" href="#"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="facebook">social_leaderboard</span></a>
<a class="text-emerald-100/50 hover:text-white" href="#"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="camera">camera</span></a>
</div>
</div>
</footer>

</Layout>
